parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle is unable to stop
the brake light comes on
the vehicle vibrates or shakes when applying brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leakage of brake fluid can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake fluid leaks from the high-pressure hose

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to a lack of protection in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle sticks
the seat belt buckle fails to fasten
the seat belt buckle releases unexpectedly
the seat belt is unable to retract.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt anchorage can cause the seat belt to detach from the floor or door, leading to a lack of protection in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt anchorage releases frequently
the seat belt detaches from the floor or door
the seat belt is inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to a lack of protection in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor is inoperative
the seat belt fails to retract
the seat belt is unable to lock securely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door hinges can cause the doors to fall off or become stuck, leading to accidents or injuries, especially if occupants are not wearing seatbelts.
symptoms: Doors fall off or become stuck
difficulty opening or closing doors
doors sag or separate from the inner part of the door
doors won't close properly
doors come off the track.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the liftgate can cause the liftgate to fall or become stuck, leading to accidents or injuries, especially if occupants are not wearing seatbelts.
symptoms: Liftgate falls or becomes stuck
difficulty opening or closing liftgate
liftgate won't close properly
liftgate comes off the track.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power locks can cause doors to become stuck or difficult to open, leading to accidents or injuries, especially if occupants are trapped inside.
symptoms: Power locks malfunction
doors become stuck or difficult to open
doors won't stay unlocked
doors must be held in the up position to open from the inside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the hood and roof can cause structural damage and lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Paint stripping off the hood and roof
